## Exceptions

The following are acceptable to run on the host:

- ✅ `docker compose` commands (build, up, down, run)
- ✅ `node scripts/*.js` diagnostic scripts
- ✅ `npx <tool>` for one-off utilities that don't modify code
- ✅ Git operations (commit, push, pull)
- ✅ File editing and code navigation

