## Environment Setup

### Prerequisites
- Docker Desktop with MCP Toolkit enabled
- Git
- Node.js 20+ (host, for scripts only)

### First-Time Setup
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/Malaccamaxgit/whatsapp-mcp-docker.git
cd whatsapp-mcp-docker

# Build containers
docker compose build

# Verify setup
docker compose run --rm tester-container npm run format:check
```

